08:31.920 --> 08:32.800
-"won’t they?
-Correct.

08:32.880 --> 08:35.200
But there has been
an unusual demand in Toledo."

08:35.360 --> 08:38.040
These last five months, have a look,
the distributor dispatched

08:38.120 --> 08:40.800
