were purchased.

09:16.400 --> 09:18.440
Get and authorization from judge Andrade

09:18.600 --> 09:20.240
"and go to that pharmacy, alone.

09:20.320 --> 09:22.720
I want you to get hold of all the lists"

09:22.880 --> 09:25.440
of purchases. And, I don’t know,
see if you can find something.

09:26.520 --> 09:29.280
-Please, don’t talk to anyone about this.
-Sure, I won’t.

09:33.280 --> 09:34.440
By the way, Raquel.

09:39.520 --> 09:40.400
