13:01.440 --> 13:04.560
I promise you that I’ll get you
out of here, my love.

13:15.240 --> 13:16.600
They’re coming in, aren’t they?

13:18.600 --> 13:19.880
Play the one of the girl.

13:19.960 --> 13:22.800
"My name is Ariadna Cascales and I’m fine,

13:23.520 --> 13:24.880
