13:25.360 --> 13:27.640
We have been treated well
by the kidnappers

13:27.720 --> 13:29.280
and I have nothing to object to."

13:29.360 --> 13:31.400
It’s today’s news report
next to the hostage.

13:32.120 --> 13:34.520
-"A kiss for my family."
-What’s the problem then?

13:34.680 --> 13:36.560
