chat, laugh, talk about my life,

15:18.480 --> 15:21.600
have a coffee, go for a walk,
go to the cinema, go dancing...

15:21.760 --> 15:23.480
"Without that order of things...

15:23.880 --> 15:26.120
honestly, I don’t see myself
sleeping with someone."

15:26.280 --> 15:28.400
-Call me old fashioned, if you want.
-"No."

15:28.560 --> 15:29.440
